<i>noun</i>: 태평 [태평], 무사태평 [무사태평] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>태평 [태평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace</dd><br>
<dd>나라가 안정되어 아무 걱정이나 탈이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a nation being peaceful without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dd>2. tranquility</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 아무 걱정이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of one's mind being serene without worries or troubles.</dd><br>
<dt>무사태평 [무사태평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace; tranquility</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 문제나 걱정거리가 없이 편안함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being peaceful without any problem or worry.</dd><br>
<dd>2. optimism</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 심각하게 생각하지 않아 근심이나 걱정이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of having no worry or concern because one does not think seriously of a matter.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>